         <div xml:id="alalal-h50713"><!-- l4d17a30 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-h50713-Hd1e99">Articulus 30</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-h50713-Hd1e101" type="question-title">An verum sit quod dicit Magister, 
Nullus debite gravioris pene accipit 
veniam ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e104">
               <pb ed="#Be" n="699"/>
               <cb ed="#Be" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#Be" n="1"/>ARTICULUS XXX.
<lb ed="#Be" n="2"/>An verum sit quod dicit Magister, 
Nul<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="3"/>lus debite gravioris pene accipit 
ve<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="4"/>niam ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e120">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="5"/>Deinde queritur de hoc quod dicitur,
<lb ed="#Be" n="6"/>ibi, A, ยง 6, ante finem: <quote xml:id="alalal-h50713-Qd1e126"> Nudlus debite
<lb ed="#Be" n="7"/>gravioris, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e132">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="8"/>1. Ibi enim nulla fit mentio de 
confes<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="9"/>sione : ergo nihil valet ad propositum.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e140">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="10"/>2. Eadem autem objectio est de 
aucto<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="11"/>ritate Hieronymi sequenti.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e147">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="12"/>3. Praeterea, queritur de hoc quod 
di<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="13"/>cit ibi Hieronymus : <quote xml:id="alalal-h50713-Qd1e153"> Dormiat in sacco. </quote>-
<lb ed="#Be" n="14"/>Videtur enim multos vere pcenitentes.
<lb ed="#Be" n="15"/>esse, et tamen linteis et non saccis 
in<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="16"/>dutos.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e163">
               <cb ed="#Be" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Be" n="17"/>Rzsponsio. Dicendum; quod vis est. in
<lb ed="#Be" n="18"/>prima auctoritate in hoc quod dicit : <quote xml:id="alalal-h50713-Qd1e171"> Etsi
<lb ed="#Be" n="19"/>longe minorem quam debeat, solverit 
poe<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="20"/>nam : </quote> poena enim minorata est per 
ef<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="21"/>fectum clavium in confessione.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e181">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="22"/>Item, in hoc est vis quod dicit, 
Solve<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="23"/>rig: quia non potest poenam solvere, nisi
<lb ed="#Be" n="24"/>ad arbitrium Ecclesie per vicarium 
Chri<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="25"/>sti fuerit taxata : aliter enim non solvit,
<lb ed="#Be" n="26"/>sed sustinet tantum poenas.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e194">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="27"/>Ad Atiup dicendum, quod Hieronymus.
<lb ed="#Be" n="28"/>facit vim in hoc quod. dicit, <quote xml:id="alalal-h50713-Qd1e200"> Ingredia-.
<lb ed="#Be" n="29"/>tur Ecclesiam : </quote> quia non potest ingredi,
<lb ed="#Be" n="30"/>nisi per poenitentiam corpori mystico
<lb ed="#Be" n="31"/>quod est Ecclesia, ostendatur reunitus :
<lb ed="#Be" n="32"/>aliter enim ingreditur numero tantum, et
<lb ed="#Be" n="33"/>non merito et veritate.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-h50713-d1e215">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="34"/>Ad aliud dicendum, quod saccus 
poni<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="35"/>tur hic pro-humilitate et asperitate 
pee<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="36"/>nitentiae, per illum tropum loquendi quo
<lb ed="#Be" n="37"/>species pro genere sepe solet poni.
</p>
